title: keskil 3 (2013)
description:
Favorite characters to a new level ! Meet the final part of the trilogy : massive , dangerous , and even more funny adventures keskilya and Vic . This time they go to distant lands, where they will treasure bequeathed keskilyu his grandfather. Upon arrival, our heroes find that they are not the only contenders for the inheritance. Loyal friends and Witek Keskil together come to the fight with rivals. But in the end it will keskilyu reveal a surprising strength, risk their lives and come together in a battle with the second contender for the fabulous legacy that will get only one !

Genre: Comedy
Country: Russia
Running time: 86 min.
Director: Alexey Egorov, Dmitry Shadrin
Starring : Michael Borisov Dmitry Shadrin Procopius Ivanov , Yegor Dem'yanov Nikita Novgorodov , Maya and other Korkin
